nt)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">SERIAL OUT</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">D-sub 9-pin (male) × 1 for link control</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">REMOTE 1 IN</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">M3 × 1 for wired remote control</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">REMOTE 1 OUT</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">M3 × 1 for link control (for wired remote control )</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">REMOTE 2 IN</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">D-sub 9-pin (female) × 1 for external control (parallel )</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">LAN</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">RJ-45 x 1 (for network and DIGITAL LINK (video/network/serial control) connection,100Base-TX, compatible with Art-Net,compliant with PJLink™,Deep Color, compatible with HDCP</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Materialidad</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">Molded plastic</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Dimensiones (W × H × D)</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">498 x 200*13 x 556 mm (19-19/32 x 7-7/8*13 x 21-7/8 in) (with supplied lens)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Peso</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">Approximately 18.3 kg (40.3 lbs) (with supplied lens)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Ruido de operación</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">40 dB (dual lamp operation, lamp mode: NORMAL),35 dB (dual lamp operation, lamp mode: ECO)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Ambiente de operación</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">Operating temperature: 0-45 °C (32-113 °F)*15,operating humidity: 10-80 % (no condensation)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Softwares</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">Logo Transfer Software,Multi Projector Monitoring &amp;Control Software,Geometry Manager Pro (included in the ET-UK20)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Accesorios incluidos</td>\r\n<td class="tb-blk">Power cord with secure lock, wireless/wired remote control unit,batteries (R03/AAA type x 2), software CD-ROM (Logo Transfer Software,Multi Projector Monitoring &amp; Control Software)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="jspVerticalBar"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
